name: Hue color candle
c8y_Notes: Classic style meets modern smart lighting features with the Philips Hue White and color ambiance E12 candelabra bulb. Use millions of shades of color and warm-to-cool white light to complement your home decor. Control instantly via Bluetooth in a single room, or pair with a Hue Bridge to unlock the full suite of smart lighting features in your whole home.
